# Brave Search MCP Server Settings
# Use this file to configure the Brave Search MCP server for Claude Desktop
#
# Format:
# SETTING_NAME=value
#
# Required Settings:
# -----------------
# BRAVE_API_KEY - Your Brave Search API key
#   Get your API key from: https://brave.com/search/api/
#   This key is required for the Brave Search MCP server to function
#
# Optional Settings:
# -----------------
# DOCKER_IMAGE - Docker image name and tag (default: mcp/brave-search:latest)
# RESTART_CLAUDE - Whether to restart Claude Desktop if it's running (true/false, default: true)
#
# Examples:
# BRAVE_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
# DOCKER_IMAGE=mcp/brave-search:custom
# RESTART_CLAUDE=false
#
# Default settings (uncomment and modify as needed):
BRAVE_API_KEY=
# DOCKER_IMAGE=mcp/brave-search:latest
# RESTART_CLAUDE=true
